@FedExHelp How about you just ring the doorbell?

@ProbablyRachel Hi Rachel this is Andre. We apologize for the inconvenience, as drivers are allowed to release packages that do not require a signature. Some may not automatically ring the bell everytime. Therefore I suggest that you may leave a note on the door stating someone is home.
